## Quick Reference

### WebIDL Types (WHATWG Encoding Standard)

| WebIDL Type | Zig Type | Notes |
|-------------|----------|-------|
| `boolean` | `bool` | JavaScript boolean |
| `byte` | `i8` | Signed 8-bit integer |
| `octet` | `u8` | Unsigned 8-bit integer |
| `short` | `i16` | Signed 16-bit integer |
| `unsigned short` | `u16` | Unsigned 16-bit integer |
| `long` | `i32` | Signed 32-bit integer |
| `unsigned long` | `u32` | Unsigned 32-bit integer |
| `long long` | `i64` | Signed 64-bit integer |
| `unsigned long long` | `u64` | Unsigned 64-bit integer |
| `float` | `f32` | IEEE 754 single precision |
| `double` | `f64` | IEEE 754 double precision |
| `encoded text` | `[]const u16` | UTF-16 string |
| `byte sequence` | `[]const u8` | Byte string (ASCII) |
| `scalar value string` | `[]const u16` | Unicode scalar value string |
| `output buffer` | `output buffer` | Binary buffer |
| `Uint8Array` | `byte array(u8)` | Typed array (13 variants) |

### Common WebIDL Operations

```zig
// Type conversions (WebIDL ¬ß3.2)
const js_num = encoding.JSValue{ .number = 42.7 };
const decoded = try encoding.decode(js_num);  // Returns 42

const js_str = encoding.JSValue{ .string = "hello" };
const dom_string = try encoding.decodeString(allocator, js_str);
defer allocator.free(dom_string);

// Error handling (WebIDL ¬ß2.8)
var result = encoding.ErrorResult{};
defer result.deinit(allocator);
try result.throwEncodingError(allocator, .NotFoundError, "Element not found");

// Buffer sources (WebIDL ¬ß2.9)
const buffer = try encoding.output buffer.init(allocator, 1024);
defer buffer.deinit();

// Collections (WebIDL ¬ß2.10)
var obs_array = encoding.ObservableArray(u32).init(allocator);
defer obs_array.deinit();
try obs_array.append(10);

// Parser (WebIDL ¬ß2)
var parser = encoding.Parser.init(allocator, idl_source);
const ast = try parser.parse();
defer ast.deinit();
```

### Common Errors

```zig
pub const WebIDLError = error{
    // Type conversion errors
    DecoderError,
    EncoderError,
    NotSupportedError,
    
    // Parser errors
    SyntaxError,
    UnexpectedToken,
    UnexpectedEOF,
    
    // EncodingError types (30+)
    NotFoundError,
    InvalidStateError,
    InvalidAccessError,
    SecurityError,
    NetworkError,
    
    // Memory errors
    OutOfMemory,
};
```

